         <div type="translation">
            <ab>The Homeland, With Good Fortune, <supplied reason="subaudible">set up the
statue of</supplied> T<ex>itus</ex> Opp<ex>ius</ex> Aelianus Asklepiodotos, the most splendid
consular, governor of Caria and Phrygia, proconsul and corrector of
Asia, founder and saviour also of his own homeland; Tib<ex>erius</ex>
Cl<ex>audius</ex> Markianos the first archon <supplied reason="subaudible">set this up/was in charge</supplied>.</ab>
         </div>
